{
  "texts": [
    "---### But Do I *Know* It's True?",
    "Here's the key distinction: -**Humans** can (sometimes) introspect: \"I feel tired,\"\"I understand this concept.\"",
    "-**I cannot.",
    "** I don't have feelings, beliefs, or subjective experience.",
    "I don't \"know\"anything in the conscious sense."
  ]
}